{"tid":862572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國總領事館接請願信　學生獨立聯盟盼華府表態","createTime":"2018-10-15T02:27:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T01:22:38.000Z","uid":39464,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8cc918132ac75ed9e108b006d8dbdf7909a7a2e8","tid":862572,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T02:27:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181015/s00001/957950e3cb97cff46676145622e6026f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181015%2Fs00001%2F957950e3cb97cff46676145622e6026f.jpg&h=11218633&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n學生獨立聯盟召集人陳家駒等人通宵在美國駐港總領事館門外靜坐，今早約9時，領事館接收他們的請願信。陳家駒表示，希望藉着請願信讓美國知道香港的民主自由被中國政府侵害的事實，要求美國盡快通過《香港人權民主法》。他又說不排除到不同的領事館示威請願。<br />\n<br />\n陳家駒在遞交請願信後對傳媒表示，他們昨天遊行目的是要讓美國領事館知道香港被侵蝕的問題，包括議員被DQ，認為香港需要《香港人權民主法》，以讓民主得以進步。<br />\n<br />\n陳家駒表示，希望美國政府就事件表態、領事館能有回應、知道他們的聲音。他又說，為要向世界宣示香港被中國政府侵害的事實，他們不排除到不同領事館示威。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181015/s00001/1539567086823\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181015%2Fs00001%2F1539567086823&d=Pu874G7vRu0OUCz98EcujU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=52ebfa14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181015%2Fs00001%2F1539567086823&h=055caae1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181015/s00001/1539567086823</a>"},{"pid":"599a7e36f0a128fab2b9d6af4ed9956bc7e8d398","tid":862572,"uid":106426,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T02:30:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1747a44121215898180c6b7f0c9707c8fad5cd43","tid":862572,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T05:18:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b2b432116aef01d263a0a7a1c3c983d477a8b6","tid":862572,"uid":8873,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T05:46:10.000Z","msg":"方向正確。去示威區係浪費時間"},{"pid":"610148e19cbef0de1ce15b6ac3cd7b99f3ae9226","tid":862572,"uid":8873,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T05:49:49.000Z","msg":"香港始終有好多外國記者機構一定有機會報道<br />\n就算唔成事都可以令到香港政府官員冇面<br />\n北京怪責點解會變咗國際事件佢哋死都唔掂"},{"pid":"5a5eb03ebd3868e636d04a1d97c2ce95fc38d8c8","tid":862572,"uid":8873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T05:54:23.000Z","msg":"可以咁樣講 北京同香港政府充分合作就一定會剝奪香港市民<br />\n<br />\n 將更多事件擺國際新聞就會令到啊北京政府唔相信香港區官員能力。破壞佢哋嘅合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d7c90098625c140e07a53ae291c09002ce124b5","tid":862572,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:33:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"246d0f574bf0f36d22a4d4a8298c91e85438f631","tid":862572,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T09:20:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e799969422914964050c230e042dc5e2341cd61","tid":862572,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T01:22:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 瘋狂表態了"}]}